Nutrient data for: CADBURY DAIRY MILK CHOCOLATE MIXED BUTTONS 115 GR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210986665
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, cocoa butter, dried skimmed MILK, dried whey (from MILK), cocoa mass, vegetable fats (palm, shea), MILK fat, emulsifiers (E442, SOYA lecithin), flavourings. MILK CHOCOLATES: MILK SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM, ACTUAL 23%.COCOA SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM. MILK CHOCOLATES CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER.**The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of milk chocolate. .
